title: Pull request merge from dohmatob/nilearn:fix-658 to nilearn/nilearn:master

text:
Thanks, you're the best to detect "leaks" ;).

Merging.

Just curious about this one: `np.dtype('i8')` is the same as `np.dtype('int')` (at least on a 64bit machine, it may well be the same as 'i4' on a 32bit machine). I don't see how this change could fix anything. Also the subject numbers are nowhere close to 2**63 ...
Sorry, what ? Better to chat face to face about this one ...
